snippet.title: CMiG | Trailer for Another War (2002)
snippet.description:
Welcome to a Polish RPG that wanted to topple Planescape: Torment... with so many bugs a knife wielding maniac could defeat a entire battalion of nazi mp40 welding soldiers ...
